snippet.textDisplay: Epic, A lot of players will agree with what I am about to say. A new DLC that gives us the ability to play on old maps (season 1-4) against bots will be a very popular decision. Fortnite just doesn't feel the same anymore with unfamiliar surroundings, Skill Based Matchmaking and lack of simplicity. I feel like the game has lost it's touch that originally brought in so many new players. For Update v13 I feel that DLC (available to all platforms), that allows us to play on all chapter 1 maps with original UI, graphics, weapons, and the ability to select double pump or glider redeploy. Most of my friends don't play anymore as it's just too hard to get wins now. If we can play on old maps with our friends against bots, a lot of players will return and the overall enjoyment rating will go up, thanks for listening.
